# PLAYER::HAS_PLAYER_DAMAGED_AT_LEAST_ONE_PED

## Summary
Returns TRUE if the player has damaged any peds since the last time that CLEAR_PLAYER_HAS_DAMAGED_AT_LEAST_ONE_PED was called

## Parameters
* **PLAYER_INDEX** player

## Returns
* **BOOL**
